      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>It's not really about a \"break\" though. It's more like... when you finish a trip, you have to leave the destination, right? You pack up and go home. But i feel like i've reached the final stop. Like there aren't any more roads left to take and the map is just blank after this. It feels more like reaching the end of the line than just needing a nap.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
