      "content": "but that's the thing... why would i want to find a new road when i'm just so done with the whole thing? it feels so heavy, like carrying all this luggage through a station that never ends. it'd be so much more peaceful to just... let go of the ticket and stop trying to find a way out. it would be so quiet if i just stopped traveling.",
