      "content": "I understand, it sounds like you're feeling overwhelmed and exhausted by the constant motion and the never-ending journey. It's okay to feel this way, and it's okay to want to stop. Remember, it's not about finding a new road or keeping going, it's about finding peace and happiness in your own way. Maybe it's time to stop trying to find a way out and just focus on taking care of yourself. You deserve to feel good and happy, no matter what you're doing. It's okay to just stop and let go of the luggage, and maybe find some quiet and peace in the stillness. You don't have to keep going, it's okay to just be.",
